{"barInfo":{"barName":"骁","description":"开放自由的类贴吧式留言板","isMainBar":true,"isPublic":true},"list":[{"author":"孙天骁","authorCode":"admin","content":"<p>骁吧是最后一个由 Vue2 / PHP 迁移到 Go + Node + Vue 3 的网站系统。</p><p>我相信经过了又一个四年的耕耘，新版骁吧将是我得意作品。</p><p>新版骁吧拥有更好的美观性、易用性和稳定性。</p><p><img src=\"/emotion/baidu/tsj/t_0003.gif\"> 也重新支持了方便的插入表情。</p><p>针对看图和图片转存做了进一步优化。</p><p>这一代骁吧，我会好好利用。也欢迎天南海北的朋友们参与讨论、提出意见和建议。</p><br><p>---</p><p>骁吧，是我在百度的个人贴吧的替代品。曾经的我是一个忠实的贴吧用户。后来经过了一些事情，我决定走上了自研的道路。之前个人贴吧上的大多数帖子都已经在 2017 年迁移到了骁吧（包括了很多黑历史，勿喷= =），它们在网站的“转载帖”标签页下。</p>","floor":1,"pid":0,"postTime":"2022-04-15 21:54:31","replyCount":0,"signKey":"","source":"","sourceUrl":"","tid":3167},{"author":"孙天骁","authorCode":"admin","content":"<p>新版骁吧支持了更加完善的提及功能。提及消息拥有实时推送到消息中心的能力。</p><p><img src=\"/s/xbar/FuoQmjtZrgxMVdO-AcQDxS4FrFQ7.jpg\"></p>","floor":2,"pid":8914,"postTime":"2022-04-15 21:56:58","replyCount":2,"signKey":"","source":"","tid":3167,"initComments":{"list":[{"author":"孙天骁","authorCode":"admin","content":"<a href=\"/u/lyq\" class=\"at-user\" data-code=\"87B69DB8EA\" target=\"_blank\">@柳宁依</a> 过来看看~","createTime":"2022-04-15 22:03:17","id":4942,"replyId":null,"replyUserCode":"","authorInfo":{"exists":true,"name":"孙天骁","code":"admin","alias":"stx","description":"一个内心丰富的人","homepageUrl":"/u/stx","group":5,"groupName":"站长","isLocked":false,"gender":1,"avatarUrl":"/s/user/FufL-vSFO5eM1we1mxdfYHKH9tfK.jpg","realName":"孙天骁","refBaike":"","isManager":true,"isMe":true,"isLover":false,"introduction":"","joinTime":"2015-02-11 21:45:00"}},{"author":"孙天骁","authorCode":"admin","content":"这是对发帖框定制程度最深的一次。","createTime":"2022-04-15 22:04:15","id":4943,"replyId":null,"replyUserCode":"","authorInfo":{"exists":true,"name":"孙天骁","code":"admin","alias":"stx","description":"一个内心丰富的人","homepageUrl":"/u/stx","group":5,"groupName":"站长","isLocked":false,"gender":1,"avatarUrl":"/s/user/FufL-vSFO5eM1we1mxdfYHKH9tfK.jpg","realName":"孙天骁","refBaike":"","isManager":true,"isMe":true,"isLover":false,"introduction":"","joinTime":"2015-02-11 21:45:00"}}],"pageInfo":{"total":2,"pageSize":10,"current":1},"total":2,"totalPages":1}},{"author":"孙天骁","authorCode":"admin","content":"<p>骁吧未来的吧内搜索、签名档和精品分类等功能已经在设想中了。未来的有一天我会把这些功能补齐。</p>","floor":3,"pid":8915,"postTime":"2022-04-15 22:01:04","replyCount":0,"signKey":"","source":"","tid":3167},{"author":"孙天骁","authorCode":"admin","content":"<p>手机版网页，也进行了大量的改进。相对四年前的版本，看帖发帖体验有明显的提升。</p>","floor":4,"pid":8916,"postTime":"2022-04-15 22:06:17","replyCount":0,"signKey":"","source":"移动版骁吧","tid":3167},{"author":"孙天骁","authorCode":"admin","content":"<p>我后面会在线上进行一些稳定性测试。然后我会下线网站之前为了能和 PHP 共同运行而编写的一些对接程序。我会发布新的文章和公众号来介绍新版的骁吧和全新的骁之屋。</p>","floor":5,"pid":8917,"postTime":"2022-04-15 22:11:21","replyCount":0,"signKey":"","source":"","tid":3167},{"author":"孙天骁","authorCode":"admin","content":"<p>我感觉我从 2017 年开始就特别喜欢网站的无刷新体验。</p>","floor":6,"pid":8918,"postTime":"2022-04-15 22:14:34","replyCount":0,"signKey":"","source":"","tid":3167},{"author":"NeoYoung","authorCode":"76FF603314","content":"<p>好强啊前辈，我自己用react做了一个网站不过才做了一个多月，希望找完工作后能做一个像大佬一样好看又强大的个人网站https://yangwe<span>﻿﻿</span>njun.cn</p>","floor":7,"pid":9026,"postTime":"2023-05-05 07:26:15","replyCount":0,"signKey":"","source":"","tid":3167}],"pageInfo":{"total":7,"pageSize":30,"current":1},"threadInfo":{"author":"孙天骁","authorCode":"admin","classifyName":"技术","goodClassifyName":"","id":3167,"isGood":true,"isPicture":true,"isRepost":false,"postTime":"2022-04-15 21:54:31","replyCount":8,"title":"“光辉号骁之屋”骁吧第一帖","topState":1},"tid":3167,"total":7,"totalPages":1,"viewHost":false,"users":{"admin":{"exists":true,"name":"孙天骁","code":"admin","alias":"stx","description":"一个内心丰富的人","homepageUrl":"/u/stx","group":5,"groupName":"站长","isLocked":false,"gender":1,"avatarUrl":"/s/user/FufL-vSFO5eM1we1mxdfYHKH9tfK.jpg","realName":"孙天骁","refBaike":"","isManager":true,"isMe":true,"isLover":false,"introduction":"","joinTime":"2015-02-11 21:45:00"},"76FF603314":{"exists":true,"name":"NeoYoung","code":"76FF603314","alias":"","description":"